Static Pages is a Rails 2.3 Engine App which allows to have instant static 
pages added to the admin.

The pages are loaded with a permalink and multiple locales are avaialable.

===============================================================================

There are a few requirements for this plugin to work:

The project must use devise (or the pages controller needs to be changed)

The project requires to use nifty_layout for the title helpers to work

RedCloth is required for the content

 